PROJECT.NAME: aBufBuf1
PROJECT.TITLE: Bufo bufo (common toad)
PROJECT.DESCRIPTION: This project collects the sequencing data and assemblies generated for Bufo bufo, common name common toad, by the Darwin Tree of Life Project (https://www.darwintreeoflife.org/). The data under this project are made available subject to the Darwin Tree of Life Open Data Release Policy (https://www.darwintreeoflife.org/project-resources/).
